title: Hopefully this meme isn't too niche

replies.body: Oh look it's that one Yorick main's alt.
Lmao no, I think that Yorick is the most boring champion in the game and I'd rather eat week old gas station sushi than play one game as him.
Just because a champions bad dosent mean they should be allowed to have a unhealthy interaction
Haha im a mord main and although its scummy, it is hilarious ti see a yorik do everything right, but then i heal to full and bonk his ass

[Link to the post I'm referencing](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/gameplay-balance/rWvcm15R-aight-morde-players-ima-need-you-to-be-reasonable-for-a-second?show=nested)

I hope I'm not violating rules somehow as it's been a while since I've done this kind of thing.
